{"timestamp":"2026-02-20 01:28:31","session_id":"2kfdjpqah8u91c5bn96tfh59jt","user_message":"How do I report an infrastructure issue?","bot_response":"**Submitting a Report - Step by Step:**\n\n1\ufe0f\u20e3 **Go to Requests Page** - Click 'Requests' in the navigation menu\n2\ufe0f\u20e3 **Select Infrastructure Type** - Choose from Roads, Street Lights, Drainage, etc.\n3\ufe0f\u20e3 **Pick Location** - Use the interactive map to mark the exact spot\n4\ufe0f\u20e3 **Describe the Issue** - Provide detailed description of the problem\n5\ufe0f\u20e3 **Upload Photos** - Add up to 4 clear images as evidence\n6\ufe0f\u20e3 **Enter Contact** - Provide your 11-digit mobile number (09XX-XXX-XXXX)\n7\ufe0f\u20e3 **Agree to Terms** - Check the box to accept our policies\n8\ufe0f\u20e3 **Submit!** - Click the submit button\n\n\ud83d\udca1 **Pro tip:** Clear, well-lit photos from multiple angles help our team respond faster!","intent":"how_to_report","confidence":0.9,"context":"home","lang":"en","ip":"::1"}
