{"timestamp":"2026-02-20 02:35:45","session_id":"a7eu88kkmr05qag4d6t3sgl8nv","user_message":"What are the Terms and Conditions?","bot_response":"**Terms & Conditions \u2014 Summary:**\n\n\ud83d\udcdc **Legal Basis:**\nGoverned by the **Data Privacy Act of 2012 (RA 10173)** and NPC regulations.\n\n\ud83d\uddc2\ufe0f **Information We Collect:**\n\u2022 User identifiers and account credentials\n\u2022 Contact info and location data for reports\n\u2022 System activity logs and timestamps\n\n\ud83c\udfaf **Purposes:**\n\u2022 System authentication and access control\n\u2022 Infrastructure reporting and coordination\n\u2022 AI-assisted decision support and analytics\n\u2022 Security monitoring and audit functions\n\n\ud83d\udd12 **Data Processing:**\n\u2022 Processed only for declared, legitimate purposes\n\u2022 Stored securely with technical safeguards\n\u2022 Deleted or anonymized when no longer needed\n\n\ud83e\udd16 **AI Disclaimer:**\n\u2022 AI recommendations are for decision support only\n\u2022 They do NOT replace human judgment or authority\n\u2022 Final decisions remain with authorized personnel\n\n\u2705 **Your Consent:**\nBy using the system, you accept these terms. You must check the consent checkbox on the submission form before submitting a report.\n\n\ud83d\udcde **Contact:**\nadmin@infragovservices.com | dpo@infragovservices.com | (02) 8988-4242\n\n\ud83d\udcc4 **Access it here:** Footer \u2192 'Terms of Service' or navigate directly to `termcon.php`","intent":"terms_conditions","confidence":0.9,"context":"privacy","lang":"en","ip":"::1"}
{"timestamp":"2026-02-20 02:37:10","session_id":"a7eu88kkmr05qag4d6t3sgl8nv","user_message":"How do I switch the language?","bot_response":"**Feature ng Pagsasalin ng Wika:**\n\n\ud83c\udf10 **Paano Magpalit ng Wika:**\n\u2022 **Desktop:** I-click ang globe icon \ud83c\udf10 na may label (EN \/ FIL) sa kanang itaas ng navigation bar\n\u2022 **Mobile:** I-tap ang globe icon malapit sa itaas ng screen\n\u2022 Agad na nagsasalin ang pahina \u2014 hindi na kailangang i-reload!\n\n\ud83c\udfaf **Ano ang Nasasalin:**\n\u2022 Lahat ng navigation menu at button\n\u2022 Nilalaman ng pahina, mga heading, at paglalarawan\n\u2022 Mga label ng form, placeholder, at tagubilin\n\u2022 Mga mensahe ng katayuan at abiso\n\u2022 Pahina ng Privacy Policy at Terms & Conditions\n\u2022 Mga mensahe ng error at kumpirmasyon\n\u2022 Mga mensahe at chips ng chatbot na ito\n\n\ud83d\udcbe **Naka-save ang Kagustuhan:**\n\u2022 Natatandaan ang iyong napiling wika sa lahat ng pahina\n\u2022 Naka-store locally \u2014 hindi kailangan ng account\n\n\ud83c\uddf5\ud83c\udded **Suporta sa Filipino:**\nBuong pagsasalin para sa lahat ng pahina:\nTahanan \u2022 Mga Ulat \u2022 Mga Kahilingan \u2022 Tungkol Sa \u2022 Privacy Policy \u2022 Terms & Conditions\n\n\ud83d\udd14 **Tandaan:** Isang toast notification (bandila + mensahe) ang nagpapatunay ng iyong pagpapalit ng wika.","intent":"language_switch","confidence":0.9,"context":"about","lang":"tl","ip":"::1"}
